+
+// ─────────────── Feature Visibility (DR-040) ───────────────
+// General feature-flag system. The code registry (lib/feature-visibility/registry.ts) owns which
+// features exist + their defaults; THIS table holds per-scope OVERRIDES only. Resolver precedence is
+// hide-wins / fail-safe. NO money logic — visibility of surfaces only; hiding never mutates ledger
+// state. Every flag change is audited via AdminAction (immutable convention).
